stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> RESERVED: Redis Lua 成功

    RESERVED --> MQ_SENT: MQ Send 确认
    RESERVED --> MQ_PENDING: Send 失败或结果未知

    MQ_PENDING --> MQ_SENT: 使用原 message_id 补发

    MQ_SENT --> ORDER_CREATED: PostgreSQL 提交成功
    MQ_SENT --> RELEASE_PENDING: PostgreSQL 永久拒绝

    RELEASE_PENDING --> RELEASED: Redis 条件补偿成功

    RESERVED --> RELEASE_PENDING: 发送恢复超时
    MQ_PENDING --> RELEASE_PENDING: 超过恢复窗口

    ORDER_CREATED --> [*]
    RELEASED --> [*]
